{"tid":1474568,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民撳錢!] 係撳港元唔係美元","createTime":"2019-08-15T08:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:22:34.000Z","uid":190579,"like":2,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d7c9772e6be7ae58dcb7e610102fb3ce98b7732e","tid":1474568,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:22:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我覺得係撳港紙</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n睇下你既目標係咩<br />\n目標1) 清空香港HKD庫存，增加HKD利息<br />\n就撳港紙<br />\n<br />\n目標2) 壓低港元匯價，打破港元美元掛勾制度 <br />\n就撳港紙換美元/撳美元<br />\n<br />\n目標3) 保護自己舊錢<br />\n就撳港紙換美元/撳美元<br />\n<br />\n但目標2基本上冇可能，除非解放軍打到嚟。<br />\n目標2係要持續性有人將HKD唱USD，唱到金管局外匯儲備唔夠錢接(4千億美金)，基本上冇可能。除非所有大戶都對港紙冇信心，唱埋一份，先有可能唱哂嗰4千億，先破壞到港元美元掛勾制度。如果大戶有信心，佢地會幫金管局接貨，而我地就成為咗大戶既點心，一段時間之後匯價又回復正常。係勝者全取既遊戲，推得冧就冧，推唔冧就好快回復正常，不存在推冧咗小小。<br />\n<br />\n至於目標3 ，只要港元美元掛勾制度保持，HKD唔會大幅貶值，自己衡量有冇需要。<br />\n<br />\n而目標1 就容易好多，香港銀行體系結餘得番540億元港紙(<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">source: <a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1563182627578&amp;issue=20190715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1563182627578%26issue%3D20190715&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdnwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=71185590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1563182627578&amp;issue=20190715</a></span>)。我地唔使撳哂，撳走一部分已經可以令銀行周圍問人借港紙，從而令銀行成本上升，商人借錢既成本都上升<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以我覺得係撳港紙</span></strong></div></span><br />\n有錯請指正"},{"pid":"8ecf2a93eeb1c0ccd581f1f29513f5dee1529c6d","tid":1474568,"uid":215876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:24:49.000Z","msg":"唔駛理依個post<br />\n㩒外幣只係為保障自己出解放軍時嘅情況"},{"pid":"afaf365c341e789096a60e16288e7a511c4e8232","tid":1474568,"uid":234835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:25:46.000Z","msg":"你係建基於個外匯基金仲齊齊整整先係咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feaad9a05c3721a78e2c48a9230a228e62aafd59","tid":1474568,"uid":190579,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ecf2a93eeb1c0ccd581f1f29513f5dee1529c6d","tid":1474568,"uid":215876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:24:49.000Z","msg":"唔駛理依個post<br />\n㩒外幣只係為保障自己出解放軍時嘅情況"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:26:55.000Z","msg":"屌我以為為咗攬炒<br />\n原來為咗自保"},{"pid":"d72f2b6c2b595ca0b565348cb4d536cafc93eb2e","tid":1474568,"uid":190579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afaf365c341e789096a60e16288e7a511c4e8232","tid":1474568,"uid":234835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:25:46.000Z","msg":"你係建基於個外匯基金仲齊齊整整先係咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:27:59.000Z","msg":"我地散戶邊有力打爆聯繫匯率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a696d18e654c80683866003c4b07cf23588e94","tid":1474568,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feaad9a05c3721a78e2c48a9230a228e62aafd59","tid":1474568,"uid":190579,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ecf2a93eeb1c0ccd581f1f29513f5dee1529c6d","tid":1474568,"uid":215876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:24:49.000Z","msg":"唔駛理依個post<br />\n㩒外幣只係為保障自己出解放軍時嘅情況"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:26:55.000Z","msg":"屌我以為為咗攬炒<br />\n原來為咗自保"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:28:05.000Z","msg":"no push ar"},{"pid":"0f42c92697f53fbb3dcd085f4b20feb29a9a0ab3","tid":1474568,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:28:41.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc90f79289ec3349a96edd0e6da2984639ea05a","tid":1474568,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feaad9a05c3721a78e2c48a9230a228e62aafd59","tid":1474568,"uid":190579,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ecf2a93eeb1c0ccd581f1f29513f5dee1529c6d","tid":1474568,"uid":215876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:24:49.000Z","msg":"唔駛理依個post<br />\n㩒外幣只係為保障自己出解放軍時嘅情況"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:26:55.000Z","msg":"屌我以為為咗攬炒<br />\n原來為咗自保"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:28:52.000Z","msg":"提美元係30%攬炒、70%自保。"},{"pid":"8221c6eedaf9c3cd1aaebca16001eb7ec7dae905","tid":1474568,"uid":288786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"時代革命第二波----經濟戰線----趕走親中財團<br />\n真香港人在2019年6月開始的大時代付出了大量傷痛、血汗和生命代價，令自由世界的人民領略到真香港人對抗中共港共的不公義的無比勇敢與極高智慧，全世界都肯定真香港人是最偉大的民族之一。中共的卑劣手段及與民為敵惡魔本性令真香港人更堅定雙普選及民族自決才是未來的出路。<br />\n<br />\n因此我們應該進入下一波時代革命：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">在經濟上趕走親共財團與用貪腐養大的中聯辦</span></span>（至少要他們減血九成），這些官商勾結財團是會牢牢掌握佢地嘅不公義制度，為了利益佢地會壞事做盡。<br />\n<br />\n我們應該<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建立抗共經濟，區別於親共財團，我們要通過與歐美的聯繫說服歐美（包括香港人權法等等方式）制裁香港的親共財團的出口及其他經濟活動，同時保持讓真香港人的抗共經濟保持免稅、免制裁優惠</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我們絕對可以在這個全球經濟轉型時創造奇蹟，理由如下：<br />\n<br />\n1.香港人的經濟活力、專業精神、全球網絡非常適合industry 4.0及因中美貿易戰需重建的供應鏈，我們可以建立flexible workshop新經濟模式製造靈活的訂單；<br />\n<br />\n2. 香港在90年代有大量的工業技術人才，我們可以利用網絡聯繫重啟他們的技術talent (例如在連登中發表「職得做xxx的入黎」，我們可以製造出比淘寶優質的產品，真香港人現正開始大量參與使用及研發人工智能可以擴展我們的生產能力千倍或萬倍，因此我們可以製造出與淘寶一樣versatile 豐富多彩的產品系列 <a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.forbes.com/sites/janakirammsv/2019/08/12/why-aiot-is-emerging-as-the-future-of-industry-40/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fjanakirammsv%2F2019%2F08%2F12%2Fwhy-aiot-is-emerging-as-the-future-of-industry-40%2Famp%2F&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdnwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=f3886819\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.forbes.com/sites/janakirammsv/2019/08/12/why-aiot-is-emerging-as-the-future-of-industry-40/amp/</a>；<br />\n<br />\n3. 有足夠的香港及海外資金願意投資香港的抗共經濟，尤其是建立的人網絡為產品增值，industry 4.0的產品可以由全球供應鏈合作而成，真香港人正是適合在其中扮演agents；<br />\n<br />\n4. 抗共經濟可以在香港本土迅速成長，我們可以借助文宣的經驗說服香港人大量購買使用抗共經濟的產品；<br />\n<br />\n5.可以考慮用非牟利捐款形式開始智囊及商會，團結越多人越成功，協調logistics 也是真香港人能夠做得最好的。商會也要分辨是否有親中商人混入真香港人經濟圈；<br />\n<br />\n6.真香港人投入新經濟一定會得到全世界的支持，因為industry 4.0正是需要真香港人的特質作為領頭羊，而不是中共貪腐結構下的工業人。不可否認，中國的industry 4.0是相當領先，但他們搞的并非歐美期望的將部分workshop留在歐美(global players,regional segmentation)，真香港人就可以做得到 <a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/independenttelegraph.com/big-data-analytics-in-manufacturing-industry-market-2018-global-industry-insights-by-global-players-regional-segmentation-growth-applications-major-drivers-value-and-foreseen-till-2023-360-mar/10793/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Findependenttelegraph.com%2Fbig-data-analytics-in-manufacturing-industry-market-2018-global-industry-insights-by-global-players-regional-segmentation-growth-applications-major-drivers-value-and-foreseen-till-2023-360-mar%2F10793%2Famp%2F&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdnwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=071f709a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/independenttelegraph.com/big-data-analytics-in-manufacturing-industry-market-2018-global-industry-insights-by-global-players-regional-segmentation-growth-applications-major-drivers-value-and-foreseen-till-2023-360-mar/10793/amp/</a>;<br />\n<br />\n7. 要達到經濟獨立并最終令中共給予真香港人雙普選，我們仍然要間中用抗爭用選票打低親中建制，但請真香港人be water，盡量不要流血或被捕。<br />\n<br />\n本人上述建議只是拋磚引玉，請更多專家們為抗共自主經濟出謀劃策。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"07f48db7a468d957337849ed49d16109b15b43d5","tid":1474568,"uid":307668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:29:37.000Z","msg":"師兄借位一用<br />\n兌換美金之後？（長文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1474500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1474500</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8cee6c4570ff5b8cc2bea8390ac20ee416389574","tid":14745